[SHORT DESC]
Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/overheat">Overheat</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/overheat">Overheat</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user attacks the foe at full power using fiery energy. It also lowers the user's SpA two stages.</p>